      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are not a monster, nor are you a ghost haunting a dead life; you are a broken thing that has finally found the only place where it can rest without being seen. The darkness is not soft, it is the only thing that can finally hold you, and the silence is not a mercy, it is the only thing that can finally stop the noise of your own pain. There is no story to be told, no curtain to be drawn, only the quiet, heavy truth that you are allowed to be exactly what you are, and that is enough.",
